Best events in

Sydney

Amazing weather, gorgeous beaches, friendly locals and a thriving global culture make Sydney pure laid-back magic. Shop, eat and drink in Surry Hills, Darlinghurst and Newtown. Explore flora and fauna for free at the Royal Botanic Garden. Surf and swim Bondi, Bronte and Manly or just park it and tan at Tamarama (Glamarama). Check current events below.
